Description: The 'bupaverse' is an open-source, integrated suite of R-packages for the handling and analysis of business process data,
    developed by the Business Informatics research group at Hasselt University, Belgium. This package is designed to facilitate the
    installation and loading multiple 'bupaverse' packages in a single step. Learn more about 'bupverse' at <https://www.bupar.net>.
